He always gets drunk and falls

866
01:12:06,522 --> 01:12:07,632
Come on. Drink...

867
01:12:07,857 --> 01:12:08,757
Mr. Representative!

868
01:12:10,459 --> 01:12:12,329
How are you? Long time no see

869
01:12:12,662 --> 01:12:13,922
Fine. I’m great

870
01:12:14,163 --> 01:12:15,423
This is my wife

871
01:12:15,665 --> 01:12:16,625
