900
01:14:21,324 --> 01:14:23,284
Have you seen breeding frogs?

901
01:14:24,293 --> 01:14:27,482
A couple of male frogs
get on one female's back

902
01:14:28,297 --> 01:14:29,286
Those male frogs...

903
01:14:29,498 --> 01:14:31,397
Do they fight one another?

904
01:14:31,734 --> 01:14:33,104
No!

905
01:14:33,502 --> 01:14:35,402
