915
01:15:34,163 --> 01:15:36,442
Why did you do this to me?

916
01:15:37,700 --> 01:15:40,330
I'm simply doing my job

917
01:16:02,491 --> 01:16:04,361
What are you laughing at?

918
01:16:04,994 --> 01:16:07,074
Damn you!

919
01:16:25,981 --> 01:16:29,670
I got you!

920
01:16:37,159 --> 01:16:38,419
Look at this

921
01:16:39,095 --> 01:16:40,995
This is my princess

922
01:16:42,631 --> 01:16:44,591
She’s pretty, isn’t she?

923
01:16:46,402 --> 01:16:48,592
Isn't she pretty?

924
01:16:49,905 --> 01:16:52,804
If you see her, please tell her...

925
01:17:56,272 --> 01:17:58,852
Why did you do this to me?

926
01:18:04,380 --> 01:18:07,600
Why did you do this to me?

927
01:18:11,720 --> 01:18:13,210
rmagirl...

928
01:18:16,492 --> 01:18:18,192
.. away from home

929
