I'm working here

930
01:18:25,467 --> 01:18:27,277
And I work very hard

931
01:18:31,207 --> 01:18:33,927
Why did you do this to me?

932
01:18:37,980 --> 01:18:40,790
Why did you do this to me?

933
01:18:57,166 --> 01:18:59,386
Evening. We're on the Sea of Japan

934
